This file describes hot install dot files on any machine.
I will try to eventually reduce manual steps for each OS, Initiall there will be a lot thougn

========================================================
MAC OSX
========================================================
I am writing these notes for OS xversion 10.8.5. I use home brew for
managing packages (http://brew.sh/) in mac
+ Install and import the theme for mac solarized theme to work
    ->https://github.com/altercation/solarized/tree/master/iterm2-colors-solarized 
+ Checkout dot files and run makesymlinks
    -> makesymlinks
+ Keyboard remap install,  Follow these instructions (may need system restart)
    -> http://stackoverflow.com/questions/127591/using-caps-lock-as-esc-in-mac-os-x

